<p>
<a name="da">@HI{{@EM{{hazu}}}}</a> indicates the speaker's belief that something will happen (or happened).

<table class="sentence">
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{@KJ{{come}}ru@EM{{hazu}}desuyo.kinou@KJ{{electricity^tale}}gaarimashitakara.}}
